=== TEST 1: test reading request body
--- config
    location /echo_body {
        lua_need_request_body on;
        rewrite_by_lua '
            ngx.print(ngx.var.request_body or "nil")
        ';
        content_by_lua 'ngx.exit(ngx.OK)';
    }
--- request eval
"POST /echo_body
hello\x00\x01\x02
world\x03\x04\xff"
--- response_body eval
"hello\x00\x01\x02
world\x03\x04\xff"



